Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku masih dianggap adik?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuho.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pacar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang, kamu adalah pacarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasa bahagianya meluap di tubuhmu, tuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya Mizuho selalu memperhatikanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, aku sangat senang\Nsaat perasaan kami berbalas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba aku jadi kangen Mizuho...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang selalu memperhatikanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukan cuma Mizuho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.67,0:01:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuho?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Shin sudah mentraktirmu makanan enak?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf banget
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuatmu ke festivalnya sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau tebus kesalahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak usah, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuho, apa terjadi sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu terdengar berusaha tegar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bertemu Kizuki\Nwaktu di festival kembang api.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh, ya, seharusnya kami sudah putus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang aku ada di markas rahasia kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pun pilihanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan selalu mendukung.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.47,0:01:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ada di sisimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo? Kamu terharu sama kebaikanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, lah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini semua,\Nkata-katamu waktu menyelamatkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang selalu memperhatikanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukan cuma Mizuho.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mulai sadar dengan jelas
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saat karyawisata kelas 6 SD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Airu juga setuju, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kobayashi dari kelas 6-3 imut, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia anak kelas 6 yang paling imut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kobayashi memang pacar idaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyamoto kelas 6-2 lebih oke, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, jangan bergadang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo pura-pura tidur!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar, cepatlah tidur!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Sempit, tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidurlah sebelah sana, Kizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang menyukai perempuan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku malah tertarik...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu menyukai Ayah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Ayah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga, kenapa harus dia, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Payah berkelahi, obrolannya membosankan pula.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria baik dan kaku yang bikin jengkel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak mengecap aku buruk\Ncuma karena mantan cewek gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang kenapa, Airu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Butuh nasihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sulit bilang ke siapa pun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa aku tertarik pada Kizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kizuki, tidak ada yang kelupaan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku tahu Kizuki selalu\N- Baju olahraga sudah dibawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- memperhatikan Mizuho.\N- Tolong periksa, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Airu? Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak ada dari pelajaran pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bolos lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia agak aneh belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga sudah jarang ke rumah Mizuho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Si Airu kelayapan ke mana, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah selesai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal kalian yang mulai duluan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Abang-Abang, sini main lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awas, dia tidak normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku ini siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membosankan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai, kebetulan banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada ketua kelas Amon, nih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau pergi bimbel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu bolos lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bawel, ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pinjam uangmu, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uangku habis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mau, lepaskan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, sedikit saja, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Airu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Airu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Amon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tahu Airu pergi ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hazawa sudah pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku bilang sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia kita jauh berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke depannya pun, mungkin kita\Ntidak akan pernah berurusan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku langsung tahu,\Nkamu sedang menahan jati diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik, Amon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan omong kosongmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sama sepertimu,\Nsedang menahan jati diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku langsung tahu,\Nkamu sedang menahan jati diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik! Berisik!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Persetan dengan jati diri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya lenyap saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pulang sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan tempat bermain\Nuntuk anak SMP sepertimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bocah sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lancang sekali para Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan pulang
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tidak punya tempat kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin meninggalkan tempat ini\Ndan pergi ke tempat lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lepaskan bajumu, duduklah di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu anak SMA?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tinggal sendirian\Ndi rumah sebesar ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibuku kabur bersama pria asing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahku bekerja tidak pulang-pulang
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan cuma menyuruhku lulus SMA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bodoh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa-bisanya membiarkan orang asing\Nmasuk ke rumahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merawat lukaku segala.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa saja mencuri uangmu dan kabur, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil kamu bisa melakukannya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang mendekatiku demi uang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang penjilat kekuasaan\Ntukang merendahkan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang ingin lari dari masalah\Ndan hidup bebas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa nilai sekali lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakai ini dan tidurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan saja kalau mau mandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bisa menilai orang lain, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu tahu isi hatiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya aku menyukai laki-laki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Konyol, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku, kamu memukul\Norang lain karena menderita.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tega mengabaikanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibanding luka tangan\Nbekas memukul orang sore tadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ucapan Touya lebih menyengat\Nke seluruh tubuhku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari itu aku pun tertidur lelap\Nsampai pagi tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka benar-benar sombong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sialan banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita bungkam kelompoknya Kenzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berurusan dengan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Airu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ponselmu berisik sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan di malam hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat angkat.\NOrang tuamu pasti khawatir, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana menurutmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat, anting-anting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena punyamu keren, aku menirunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Modelnya sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gila!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyaman sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sok-sokan, Airu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan besar kepala\Nhanya karena Touya menyukaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami tidak pernah menganggapmu\Nsebagai kawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukanlah tempatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, tapi kamu tidak punya tempat\Nuntuk pulang juga, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Siapa suruh dia sombong?\N- Kejam sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ngeri banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana cara supaya aku hilang?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Airu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kamu datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu baik-baik saja?\NKok luka-luka begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo ke rumah sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibumu dan yang lainnya juga\Nmengkhawatirkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuho, jadilah pacarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat membenci diriku yang sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat kembali pun tidak punya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau berpacaran denganmu,\Naku merasa bisa berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asalkan aku bisa mencintai Mizuho\Nlayaknya pada Kizuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, perasaanmu padaku bukanlah cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski bukan pacarmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan selalu berada di sisimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan selalu mendukungmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sinilah tempatmu kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuho...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, tidak tahu harus berbuat apa lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ekspresinya kocak banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kalian?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi, apa kalian kenal Izumi Airu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya ada yang melihat dia di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sedang mencarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian teman-temannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tahu, tolong beri tahu kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Airu sudah lama tidak pulang ke rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peduli amat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak bilang alasannya tidak pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sudah tidak tahu lagi harus apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Setidaknya...\N- Hei, Kizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Iya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian, siapanya dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia teman masa kecilku yang berharga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak bilang apa-apa padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku paham setelah melihat kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia ketakutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketakutan saking sayangnya
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terhadap kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terjadi tawuran remaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beberapa orang melarikan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei! Berhenti!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lari ke mana dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah paham, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia kita jauh berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan memaksakan diri lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kembalilah ke sisi teman-teman masa kecilmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kamu bicarakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka seenaknya memulai perkelahian\Nke kelompok Kenzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku berniat memanggilmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu polisi datang...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua ini tidak ada hubungannya denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada hubungannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ikut!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, apa kamu masih bisa\Nbilang hal yang sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan macam-macam, tenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan menyentuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu menyukai orang bernama Kizuki itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, hadapilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bukan orang yang akan lari\Nmeski kamu menyatakan perasaan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhentilah menutupi\Nkepengecutanmu sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mendekati kami lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bukan orang yang akan lari\Nmeski kamu menyatakan perasaan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang selalu memperhatikanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukan cuma Mizuho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencintaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf mengejutkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Airu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudahlah, jangan katakan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa berpacaran denganmu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena aku mencintai Mizuho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:22:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu orang yang berharga bagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Esok hari pun, aku ingin\Nberangkat sekolah bersamamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergi ke pantai lagi, saling bercerita\Ndengan canda tawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bolehkah aku tetap berada di sisimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan selalu berada di sisimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Airu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah tidak berpikir\Nuntuk melenyapkannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diriku yang sebenarnya.
